{"tid":1439393,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好補Oscar ma!","createTime":"2019-08-10T05:44:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-30T07:40:30.000Z","uid":302432,"like":78,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"a4643a17aaaa7b040af1f0669f32215307c012f4","tid":1439393,"uid":302432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:44:16.000Z","msg":"小妹上年報過一期Oscar ma<br />\n想分享少少感想<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">個人認為補佢有兩樣好處既</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1</span> 平 同friend一齊補 一期只係400蚊 兩本筆記<br />\n而且可以係屋企睇片 唔洗去補習社<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2</span> 筆記例子好多 9成都係冇聽過既例子<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">但係我覺得補完都係冇用</span><br />\n<br />\n一期有超過三十條片 每條片都超過30分鐘<br />\n一開頭覺得好好 一路追佢啲片黎睇<br />\n<br />\n但之後要顧及其他科 根本好難抽時間睇佢既片<br />\n<br />\n而且佢既片有好多廢話 又冇得用1.5倍速去睇<br />\n<br />\n佢成日用唔同既螢光筆去highlight  扮到好有系統 但係其實間完冇乜意思<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我用一年時間都未睇矖佢既片 因為覺得廢話實在太多 所以唔睇<br />\n<br />\n佢教既議題一個都冇貼中都算喇 答題技巧又冇用<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我交過一份功課比佢 比我平時做學校功課更用心去寫<br />\n<br />\n佢最後竟然比level 2我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我係學校既predicted grade係攞 5/5*<br />\n<br />\n呢個都係其中一個原因我冇繼續補佢 太打擊我自尊心！<br />\n<br />\n你亂咁改不如比u我！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以 如果你想補Oscar ma請你三思 需要有自制能力去睇片 而且要預左唔會睇得曬佢啲片(我冇一個friend可以睇曬) <br />\n例子雖然好多 但好難背 如果考試唔係出同一個議題都用唔番<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後！<br />\n個人認為通識唔需要補習 平時睇新聞記低例子<br />\n考dse既時候都只係考前一日先溫LS <br />\n係信報通識抄低啲例子數據<br />\n考試時盡量嘔出黎<br />\n有幾個相關例子就會好高分架喇<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申:我dse攞5*<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />收皮啦！Oscar ma"},{"pid":"2190763ccec86d3ef2fdb728e14dc4fd9873f2f3","tid":1439393,"uid":176910,"like":67,"dislike":2,"score":65,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:49:02.000Z","msg":"依家仲有人去補佢我真係沒野講？定你西痕想被佢屌"},{"pid":"50f2a5c137c082d9646ecd6226c676b91ff55e41","tid":1439393,"uid":302432,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"2190763ccec86d3ef2fdb728e14dc4fd9873f2f3","tid":1439393,"uid":176910,"like":67,"dislike":2,"score":65,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:49:02.000Z","msg":"依家仲有人去補佢我真係沒野講？定你西痕想被佢屌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:53:58.000Z","msg":"係網上睇片架 感覺仲有好多人補"},{"pid":"930b136c490b364bbd79b027794d10fa51ad2589","tid":1439393,"uid":302649,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T08:20:14.000Z","msg":"補YY Lam 咪好，我而家人生5***。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(中文攞2，做大專生，人生5**+1分=5***)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#yup"},{"pid":